    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市区间波动，金价创历史新高：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-20/asian-stocks-to-rise-after-wall-street-win-streak-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市涨跌互现，投资者等待进一步的交易催化剂。由于中东紧张局势刺激需求，投资者为美国总统大选做准备，黄金价格创下历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-20/asian-stocks-to-rise-after-wall-street-win-streak-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 20 Oct 2024 22:39:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲 IPO 大热周或创 2022 年以来最大周度纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-20/asian-ipos-set-for-blockbuster-week-as-animal-spirits-return</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市正准备迎接两年多以来最繁忙的上市周，这对企业在美国大选前筹集资金的需求来说是一个至关重要的考验。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-20/asian-ipos-set-for-blockbuster-week-as-animal-spirits-return</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 20 Oct 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
